column5: How much a litre should I expect to pay in the Kenora area in the next few weeks?? I will be up in 2 weeks. I'll be buying anyway but would like to know for the budget. Thanks in advance.
Dryden was $1.089 per liter on May 27th.
It is still $1.08 per liter today.
It is still $1.08 per liter today.
